Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.82,0:01:58.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That sonuvabitch... hit me on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:08.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I won't let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:24.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Akina's potato is keeping up with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.90,0:02:35.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}That little...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.83,0:02:43.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't screw around with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:13.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,His turn-in is unbelievably fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.35,0:03:16.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Brake lights...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.54,0:03:19.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,His brake lights are on during\Nhigh speed cornering?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.87,0:03:28.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Damn, I can't keep up with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.49,0:03:30.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}He's got incredible technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:36.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The turn-in of that EG6 might\Nbe faster than Takumi's.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:39.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.83,0:04:06.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Thank you very much!{\r}\NThank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:11.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,And he really pissed me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:15.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Braking while cornering?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:17.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,And at high speed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:18.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:20.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen anything\Nlike it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:25.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?  It happens often.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:29.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I brake in corners so often.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:36.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh shit, I'm too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:38.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared, tap, tap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:41.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't having such a\Nlow level conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:46.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That EG6 cleared the corner\Nat a very high speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:49.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,EG6?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:52.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Civic.\NA Civic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:56.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you\Nsimply say Civic?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:05:00.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Although the Civic is FF,\Nit's popular among Road Racers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.89,0:05:05.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got a 1.6 liter, non-turbo engine\Nlike the Eight-Six...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.23,0:05:10.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it's very powerful thanks\Nto its VTEC engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.98,0:05:15.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Civics and Levin/Truenos have\Nbeen rivals for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:19.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't neglect the Civic because\Nyou're driving an Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:25.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't yield to the Civic\Nbecause I drive the Levin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:33.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I can't believe how he braked after\Na high speed entry into a corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.29,0:05:37.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's using a left foot\Nbraking technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:40.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Left foot braking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:44.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't use that technique\Nwith FR cars very often.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:49.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can use your left foot for braking\Nfor sensitive control at the limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:55.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,FF cars like the EG6 experience understeering\Nwhen you step on the gas pedal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:59.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an advanced technique, when\Nwhile depressing the gas pedal...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.31,0:06:03.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...they use left foot braking to lessen the\Nrear load and stay on the ideal path.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:09.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If he used that, he must be\Na really good FF driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:12.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be very fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:17.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's fast, but that sonuva...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.09,0:06:23.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to avoid an accident because\NI practiced spinning using the parking brake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:26.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,My S13 could've been\N"hospitalized" again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.73,0:06:31.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't get away the\Nnext time I see that EG6!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:42.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.72,0:06:43.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.83,0:06:46.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you had a phone call a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:46.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,From who?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:48.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.\NIt was a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:52.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,She was cute.\NShe said she'd call back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.03,0:06:56.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know if she's cute or\Nnot by talking on the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:07:00.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Being a man for a long time,\Nmy instincts can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:03.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Experience counts in both women and cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:05.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:05.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:10.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better go to the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.48,0:07:34.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, this is Fujiwara Tofu Shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.02,0:07:36.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Hello, Takumi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:37.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Mogi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:39.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Sorry.\NWere you sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:41.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}It's about our plans...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.32,0:07:59.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this had better not\Nbe a joke, Takumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.74,0:08:04.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If it turns out to be,\Nit'll end our friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:08.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's coming with another girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.87,0:08:10.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.23,0:08:13.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Mogi definitely said\Nshe'd bring her friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.83,0:08:16.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she'll be cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:21.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice body or maybe incredibly beautiful?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:22.59,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.59,0:08:26.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. She's Mogi's\Njunior high friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.26,0:08:29.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm not so picky\Nabout her looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:32.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If I keep my hopes too high,\NI might be disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.93,0:08:37.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So you kept your promise, Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:40.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy to have\Na good friend like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.73,0:08:42.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're overreacting...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:43.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.28,0:08:47.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,With a girl by my side,\NI'll be the fastest on Akina!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.45,0:08:51.61,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.61,0:08:53.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:55.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,My Levin, my...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:08:59.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,They should be here by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.40,0:09:02.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi, did you wait long?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:05.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Mogi, don't surprise me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:08.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll introduce you.\NThis is friend Saori.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:10.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Takumi and Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:15.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.58,0:09:16.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:22.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Cute babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.26,0:09:31.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're a Road Racer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:32.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?  Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:35.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on the team called\Nthe Akina Speedstars.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.23,0:09:39.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm number three or four.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.17,0:09:43.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Akina's Levin is\Nwell known in Gunma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:45.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.05,0:09:47.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What's a Road Racer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:48.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:50.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know, Natsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:51.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Road Racers are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:55.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Way to go, Saori.\NShe's better than I hoped for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:57.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Itsuki, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:06.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I drive?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.78,0:10:08.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:11.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.\NIt's a bad Road Racer habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.74,0:10:26.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:28.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.09,0:10:33.81,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,His driving is so rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.81,0:10:36.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takumi and Natsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.35,0:10:40.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.75,0:10:43.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you guys take a ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.46,0:10:49.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,They're getting along well, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.00,0:11:21.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I could take you guys home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.92,0:11:23.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:26.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't seen each other for a while,\Nso we want to talk more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.84,0:11:29.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsuki, thank you.\NIt was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.78,0:11:31.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,See you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:35.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.84,0:11:37.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,S...Saori...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.45,0:11:42.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Saori, see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:11:57.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Great, great, great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.79,0:11:59.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:05.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about Saori.\NI feel so alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:07.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Saori!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:10.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, drive carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.80,0:12:12.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.43,0:12:15.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much, Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.27,0:12:22.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,She said "again."\NI'll ask her to go driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:24.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.66,0:12:40.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.63,0:12:49.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.88,0:12:55.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, is there anything else to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.16,0:12:56.81,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Work, work...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:13:01.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsuki's so excited.\NI wonder if he found a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:01.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.74,0:13:05.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, I won't forgive him\Nfor getting ahead of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.08,0:13:07.59,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Takumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:11.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...do you feel like driving my S13?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.57,0:13:16.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's refreshing to drive a\Ndifferent car once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.45,0:13:19.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thanks.\NI'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:22.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's your precious...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.72,0:13:24.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you, Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:27.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to learn from your driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.89,0:13:29.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.56,0:13:47.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Shingo, are you serious about\Nracing Akina's Eight-Six?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:50.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:56.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:09.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}C'mon, Akina's Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.43,0:14:11.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I'm looking forward to seeing you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:19.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:21.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you, Takumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.28,0:14:23.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Just drive normally and I'll be satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:25.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be very helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:27.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, just this once!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.94,0:14:29.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.31,0:14:34.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't driven other cars, so I don't\Nthink I can drive it fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:37.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Iketani's only asking this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.36,0:14:38.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you drive?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:40.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:41.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Give him a little respect!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:44.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright then, just this once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:46.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't expect too much, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.50,0:14:48.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you will?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:50.61,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.09,0:14:56.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky you, Iketani.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.88,0:14:58.81,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pass out, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.81,0:15:02.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, don't worry.\NThis is the second time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.41,0:15:03.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Push it hard, Takumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:05.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.94,0:15:06.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:18.77,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:22.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... how about braking drift?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:23.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.09,0:15:29.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,H...hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.87,0:15:32.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna do it right away...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:38.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,A...aren't we going too fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.31,0:16:13.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Iketani will be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:16.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Or once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.21,0:16:19.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll witness...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:24.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...the echoing death cry on the frightening\NMt. Akina downhill...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.57,0:16:27.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...as Iketani, in the third corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:31.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...p...p...p...passes out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.13,0:16:34.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it happen again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.97,0:16:50.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I...incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:52.81,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}He's drifting a car he's\Ndriving for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.22,0:16:57.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Is my S13 actually this fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:17:00.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's different from my car...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.21,0:17:03.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I've got the hang of\Nhow to drive this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.13,0:17:06.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,B...but you only cleared\Nthe third corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.64,0:17:09.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes the drift.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.16,0:17:10.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Drift...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.52,0:17:12.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Then until now...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.26,0:17:46.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I turned the corner\Nas I imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:49.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Incredible...\NHe's so incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:51.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I don't know what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:12.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,They're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:20.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're still conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.73,0:18:22.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You've improved a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.38,0:18:28.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Iketani, did you get any hints\Nfor braking drift?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.88,0:18:30.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He?  Not a one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:32.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.06,0:18:33.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:36.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What was the point of asking\NTakumi for the favor then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.48,0:18:38.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you say so, Kenji...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:43.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...Takumi performs incredible\Ntechniques so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.40,0:18:48.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I "learned" that his level is totally different,\Nand I can't learn from him yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:50.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a big improvement.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.68,0:19:06.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,An EG6!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:08.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's the one from last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.40,0:19:44.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonuva...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:47.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.64,0:19:51.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You hit my car from\Nbehind, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.89,0:19:53.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:55.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.47,0:19:57.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You remember this two-tone S13, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:20:00.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.36,0:20:01.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:05.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize!  You could've caused\Na big accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:09.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break.\NIt was your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:10.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.26,0:20:14.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You were so slow I couldn't\Npredict your actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:17.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect you to enter\Nthe corner so slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:21.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't brake in time,\Nand I touched your tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.29,0:20:22.76,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:24.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Iketani!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.84,0:20:26.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What an asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.90,0:20:30.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Iketani's pride is torn to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:35.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want me to apologize,\Nwe'll race by our rules...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.03,0:20:38.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...and if you win, I'll kneel\Ndown to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:41.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,By your rules?\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.65,0:20:43.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not so difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:47.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We call it a gumtape death match.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:50.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Gumtape death match?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.13,0:20:55.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Just bind your right hand to the\Nsteering wheel with gumtape.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:56.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.97,0:20:59.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We race under those conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:03.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Bind the right hand to the\Nsteering wheel with gumtape?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:05.77,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The left hand is free for shifting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.77,0:21:07.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The right hand to the steering wheel...
